## Example Phrases

  - **No hay rosa sin espina.**
    - Every rose has its thorn. (There is no rose without a thorn.)
  - **Donde hay humo, hay fuego.**
    - Where there’s smoke, there’s fire.

## Dichos

  - **ha habido...**
    - there has been..., there have been...
  - **había...**
    - there was..., there were...
  - **habrá...**
    - there will be...
  - **habría...**
    - there would be...
  - **hubo...**
    - there was..., there were...



