  - I hear the voice of a friend.

- **¡Oye!**
  - Hey!

- **¡Oigo!**
  - Hello! (on the telephone)

## Proverbs

- **Las paredes tienen oídos. (Las paredes oyen.)**
  - The walls have ears.

- **A palabras locas, oídos sordos.**
  - Turn a deaf ear to crazy words.

